    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This Porsche 996 Carrera 2 represents a balanced entry into analog performance. It features the 3.4L water-cooled flat-six engine with a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis retains its communicative hydraulic steering rack and neutral handling characteristics, supported by a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension. Braking is handled by factory four-piston monobloc calipers over ventilated rotors, showing no signs of fade. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals remain robust, offering a high-revving, rear-engine experience for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
